The,TM,Forum,Service,Problem,Management,API,is,designed,for,use,by,service,providers,that,require,a,solution,for,monitoring,problems,in,their,service,areas,The,API,responds,to,service,problems,triggered,by,partners,or,event,information,notifications,sent,by,infrastructure,providers,Such,event,information,notifications,may,include,alarm,performance,anomalies,trouble,ticket,SLA,violations,maintenance,and,prediction,The,API,conveys,requests,and,responses,in,JSON,format,It,is,currently,a,beta,release